---
description: Bookmark session save/resume
globs: []
alwaysApply: false
---
When user says "bookmark this" or "save session":
Run: `bookmark save --source cursor --transcript-stdin -m "<current goal>"`
Pipe recent messages as JSON-lines to stdin.

When user says "resume [name]" or "what was I working on":
Run: `bookmark resume [name or latest]`
